			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Discuss Key Takeaways from Workshop 1 and what participants wanted to learn more about">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Revisit the goals in your Project Plan and discuss what information you might need to meet these goals">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Learn about local and online data options for hazards, equity, and resilient systems">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Estimate your team’s capacity for collecting data using the Scoping Information Gathering document">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="•	Decide what data sources to use and who on the core team will be the point person for hazards, equity, and resilient systems data">
